          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "then let my enemies capture me. Let them trample me into the ground and drag my honor in the dust. Interlude "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "then let my enemies capture me. Let them trample me into the ground and drag my honor in the dust. Interlude"
